src_original: gzhag pa ni la ma'o/_/chos dran pa nye bar gzhag pa ni dum skyes ma'o/_/ sems dran pa nye bar gzhag pa ni gzugs can ma'o/_/'dun pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi
tgt_original: vedanānusmṛtyupasthānasvabhāvā lāmā |  dharmānusmṛtyupasthānasvabhāvā khaṇḍarohā |  cittānusmṛtyupasthānasvabhavā rupiṇīti jñānacakram |

src_original: rkang pa ni/_rab gtum ma'o/_/brtshon 'grus kyi rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa ni gtum mig ma'o/_/dpyod pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa ni 'od ldan ma'o/_/sems kyi rdzu
tgt_original: chandaṛddhipādasvabhāvā pracaṇḍā |  vīryaṛddhipādasvabhāvā caṇḍākṣī |  mīmāsāṃṛddhipādasvabhāvā prabhāvatī |

src_original: 'phrul gyi rkang pa ni sna chen ma'o/_/dad pa'i dbang po ni dpa' bo'i blo ma'o/_/
tgt_original: cittaṛddhipādasvabhāvā mahānāsā |  śraddhendriyasvabhāvā vīramatī |  vīryendriyasvabhāvā kharvarī |

src_original: brtshon 'grus kyi dbang po ni mi'u thung ma'o/_/dran pa'i dbang po ni lang ga'i dbang phyug ma'o/_/ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang po ni shing grib ma'o/_/shes rab
tgt_original: smṛtīndriyasvabhāvā laṅkeśvarī |  samādhīndriyasvabhāvā drumacchāyeti cittacakram |  prajñendriyasvabhāvā airāvatī |

src_original: kyi dbang po ni sa srungs ma'o/_/dad pa'i stobs ni 'jigs byed chen mo'o/_/
brtshon 'grus kyi stobs ni rlung shugs ma'o/_/dran pa'i stobs ni chang 'thung ma'o//
ting nge 'dzin gyi stobs ni sngo bsangs ma'o/_/shes rab kyi stobs ni shin tu bzang mo'o/_/ting nge 'dzin yang dag byang chub kyi yan lag ni rta sna ma'o/_/
